{"tid":2029954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家將524 行動正名為反國安法大遊行","createTime":"2020-05-22T13:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T09:23:29.000Z","uid":262035,"like":101,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a23bfd0ac4db1b3599284f8716d07b79ed555a38","tid":2029954,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"本身個行動係由匿名手足提出嚟<br />\n並唔存在搞手去修訂活動主題同細節<br />\n<br />\n而家好明顯國安法係比國歌法嚴重同迫切好多<br />\n係本土同國際間都有更大迴響<br />\n所以好應該藉住呢個時機將主題改為反國安法<br />\n去吸引更多人出嚟同國際既關注<br />\n<br />\n為活動正名好重要<br />\n一來可以令淺黃人士感受到迫切性要行出嚟<br />\n二來可以幫國際社會聯繫活動同國安法，有助打國際線<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨分享下諗法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將活動正名做反國安法大遊行 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫返反惡歌法大遊行算啦"},{"pid":"2b1498970f652814cc7b8a81e82c623a56b5d405","tid":2029954,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"both"},{"pid":"d3b064f720fa2735c56767846c15432418d4e5e3","tid":2029954,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"226b3650f228155d1b676584d3ae5d50bf68d1be","tid":2029954,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2b1498970f652814cc7b8a81e82c623a56b5d405","tid":2029954,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"both"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"不過有時太多主題會失焦<br />\n反國安法其實都反埋國歌法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8feeeff2a975aba9aa69990b3b49c4aa3d19ff","tid":2029954,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"活動正名好重要<br />\n對文宣同國際線都好大幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8025668cc353ccdf70748f6597f961c824fd5770","tid":2029954,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2338e6d39801aff6110deee42029cf0cc0fd95ff","tid":2029954,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"524 反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf43574fd48b3057b8432214265fa126849e96","tid":2029954,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962a4f24549b0689d6a45b04bd438f1127ae87ea","tid":2029954,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"覺得有道理既幫手推推po<br />\np牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"996c33cb16ff74ceb9583677d0d853edc7ff48dd","tid":2029954,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897ef501563a9c521e9b1481a28f86c6f1f62dc7","tid":2029954,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbc1bd41f0e28e94251c68494c6df923ab73bbe4","tid":2029954,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0